-- UBS Appoints John Mathews Head of Private Wealth Management
-- B y   L a u r a   M a r c i n e k
-- 2013-05-03T20:49:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-03/ubs-appoints-john-mathews-head-of-private-wealth-management.html
UBS AG, Switzerland’s biggest bank,
named John Mathews head of private wealth management,
responsible for its Americas’ ultra-high-net-worth business.  Mathews was most recently regional director for the U.S.
Southeast region, UBS said today in an e-mailed statement. In
his new role, he’s responsible for all private wealth-management
offices in the country, the Zurich-based firm said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Laura Marcinek in  New York  at 
 lmarcinek3@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
